Interface SortedList<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CarlSortedList

    public interface SortedList<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>
    SortedList interface adapted from Carrano 16.4 and java.util.List. A sorted list ADT is like a list, but maintains its entries in sorted order (rather than in the order they were inserted or the order that the user specified).
